  <brief_title>H. Pylori Eradication on Healing of Iatrogenic Gastric Ulcer by Endoscopic Mucosal Resection</brief_title>
  <official_title>Helicobacter Pylori Eradication Therapy on the Healing of Iatrogenic Gastric Ulcer After Endoscopic Mucosal Resection of Gastric Neoplastic Lesions: a Multicenter, Randomized, Double Blind, and Placebo Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
