  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the effect of Helicobacter pylori eradication therapy on the healing
      of iatrogenic gastric ulcer caused by endoscopic mucosal resection of gastric neoplastic
      lesions and is a multicenter, randomized, double blind, and placebo controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
